{"tid":1734154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有無人有相機可以借］日本記者昨逃命時遺失相機 佢想借相機今晚係集會拍短片","createTime":"2019-11-18T09:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T10:34:47.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1701cce5a6a01afa7825587f14781bb50e043f75","tid":1734154,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"#毒者求助<br />\n急 【日本記者於理工逃命時遺失相機】<br />\n<br />\n日本自由身記者大袈裟太郎(Togo Inomata)，昨日理工之役遺失了相機，他今晚將會參與尖沙咀集會，希望香港人可以幫忙，讓他完成採訪工作。<br />\n<br />\n大袈裟太郎さん由6月開始已經係最前線一直以自由身身分採訪，在twitter擴散很多日本不會報導的消息給關心香港的日本人知道。很不幸，在10月13日採訪尖沙咀人鏈時被偷走iPhone11 pro，10月15日GPS最後出現地點在黃大仙，他傷心欲絕停止香港採訪回日本。<br />\n<br />\n但見到這幾天香港的情況，他不忍心日本媒體不作深入採訪，於是在11月17日(昨天)再次來到香港採訪，一到步就直接去理工大學，拍攝了很多相片當中更有一段日文訪問學生的短片。(<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100001985243462/posts/2483796821696468?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100001985243462%2Fposts%2F2483796821696468%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=c1ab05a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100001985243462/posts/2483796821696468?sfns=mo</a>)<br />\n<br />\n很遺憾，在混亂期間他遺失了Nikon D3300相機。他今天晚上會參加尖沙咀集會，希望各位香港人可以幫忙，借器材或給他一些援助，讓他可以繼續香港的採訪，讓更多日本人知道香港的情況。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter : <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/oogesatarou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Foogesatarou&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=fbf841d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/oogesatarou</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/oogesa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Foogesa&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=89277267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/oogesa</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/536238626565200/posts/1206302509558805?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F536238626565200%2Fposts%2F1206302509558805%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=67e3bc3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/536238626565200/posts/1206302509558805?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"91c0ba3252661fb5ef1d6dc59c5b2d7fc128b21a","tid":1734154,"uid":150325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:32:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"abf46334b19f717f552bd34eefe3f89bf42a7c5d","tid":1734154,"uid":218684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7092df878c159da59c3de75e8089c822c18f0827","tid":1734154,"uid":189015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:33:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f8837a29f551c7305c24f5c524c8db097c2ddc6","tid":1734154,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"03d92159fe23334dbca5dfd7ee5951e2935a0443","tid":1734154,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca73c69a2b91429214a04c807ad6ca47c9aabb78","tid":1734154,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"推吓"},{"pid":"772937c7da7a24851247a2a7a99f5b60dd842ad4","tid":1734154,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:34:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"19af4368f42cfb63c583943e00a9a8118d07d428","tid":1734154,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"推，咁遲先睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}